      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/un-security-council-adopts-resolution-phasing-down-peacekeeping-mission-dr-congo-2023-12-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国安理会周二一致通过一项决议，开始逐步结束在刚果民主共和国的维和任务。]]></description>
